        "found": true,
        "localization": {
          "name": "Electrotoxin",
          "description": "If this unit would be defeated by an enemy attack or a status effect while having more than 1 HP, it instead survives with 1 HP.\n\nEach time this unit takes damage from an attack and survives until after the end of the turn with more than 1 HP, this unit will Stun all enemies for 50TU and Super Poison all enemies. This effect cannot trigger if this unit is alone on the battlefield. This is not a Skin passive skill."
        }
      },
